&lt;p&gt;As the Engineering Manager, within Guest &amp;amp; Host Services, you’ll lead a team of talented, diverse software developers to prototype, build and improve hosting services, balancing the shorter term business outcomes along with longer term technical stability, scalability and flexibility aligning with cross functional partners.&lt;/p&gt;
