&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Senior Business Solutions Engineer&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Business Technology Enablement and Innovation team, within the BizTech organization, leads the mission to deliver innovative technology, empowering our employees to utilize technology productively, driving connection, and scale support for employees. We bridge the gap between traditional IT and engineering teams by providing quick solutions, consultations, and guidance beyond traditional support, with a focus on enhancing workflows and tools utilizing AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a world-class Senior Business Systems Engineer to join our dynamic team. You will be responsible for providing quick solutions utilizing internal tools and agentic AI, to support and assist teams in enhancing their day to day workflows, overseeing the end-to-end delivery of system and tool changes as required, and providing support to those solutions.. Your expertise will help identify current pain points for stakeholders, promote industry best practices, and maintain data integrity and accuracy within our platforms. You will also play a crucial role in mentoring junior team members, driving strategy, and delivering results with excellence. A high degree of focus on practical AI and understanding the current state of industry as AI technology changes is critical.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;A Typical Day:&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Roadmap Ownership&lt;/strong&gt; - Lead the design, development, implementation, and optimization of custom solutions to improve internal teams’ processes and workflows, with a focus on Agentic AI solutions utilizing Airbnb approved internal tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stakeholder Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Identify and address current pain points, socialize industry best practices, and prioritize project pipelines in collaboration with stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automation&lt;/strong&gt; - Identify and drive automation initiatives to reduce manual processes and improve operational efficiency across core business functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vendor Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Partner with our vendors to drive and own the product feature and bug lifecycle from requirements gathering to launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Industry Trends - Stay updated with the latest platform features, best practices, and industry trends to proactively identify opportunities for enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Process Improvement &lt;/strong&gt;- Craft and suggest future-state business processes, and lead the implementation of these suggestions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expertise and Mentorship &lt;/strong&gt;- Act as a company-wide expert in relevant functional tools and applications. Mentor junior team members and provide guidance on development and delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architecture and Design Reviews &lt;/strong&gt;- Collaborate on architecture and design reviews, offering necessary guidance to ensure development guidelines are followed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of professional experience&amp;nbsp; with proven enterprise-grade systems implementations, IT consulting or similar field leveraging advanced platform integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 2 years of experience demonstrably using AI in workflows and to support customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience researching and implementing custom applications from the Marketplace from research, to design and implementation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced degree (e.g., MS/MBA) in Business, Computer Science, or related fields preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience designing and implementing custom business solutions and integrations using enterprise platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge of data modeling, business intelligence tools (e.g., Tableau), and enterprise reporting best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at stakeholder engagement and cross-functional collaboration in large global organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adept at leading complex projects, simplifying technical concepts, and promoting operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills, especially in critiquing technical designs and leading workshops, and engaging with senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exemplifies strong leadership fundamentals, guides junior team members, and drives strategy with a focus on long-term scalability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in designing and implementing data management strategies to ensure data integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies opportunities for product and process improvements and can lead and implement said improvements, obtaining necessary buy-in from stakeholders and leadership..&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;The Communications team is responsible for telling the Airbnb story around the world. Whether we are briefing press on inspiring travel trends, highlighting unique stories about our hosts, or explaining how travel on our platform benefits local families and communities, we are the voice of Airbnb on a broad range of topics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The Senior Communications Lead, DACH &amp;amp; CEE will lead communications strategy in Germany while providing strategic oversight across the broader DACH region and select Central and Eastern European markets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Reporting into the EMEA Communications Director, the role will strategically lead the DACH communications team, which is made up of a team of four people, including consumer, corporate comms, and an influencer manager focused on the region. We also have agency partners in Germany, Switzerland and Central &amp;amp; Eastern Europe, and successful management of these agency partners will be key to the role. This role will also be required to collaborate closely with the Country Manager for DACH and CEE&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The core focus of the role is to create industry-leading strategies and campaigns that can deliver against the local business goals and the global comms priorities. This role is for a communicator who has solid experience in delivering campaigns and strategies that will inspire the team and the wider organization, and create a vision for the way that we seek to promote the Airbnb brand and products to a range of audiences.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The role spans our corporate and policy work, where we face some regulatory challenges, as well as our consumer campaigns where we need to deliver strategies that will drive both brand awareness and positive sentiment. The role demands high level expertise in both consumer and corporate communications, with the adaptability to switch between each area regularly and apply best in class thinking to challenges and opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The right candidate will already be recognised as a leader in their field at this level, with a proven track record of using a range of comms strategies and disciplines to solve complex and ambiguous problems. They will also have a history of delivering projects across cross-functional teams, taking a strategic leadership role and anticipating challenges. The right candidate will also be expected to demonstrate a working knowledge of how to translate a global brand proposition to a local audience across the DACH markets. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;You must be comfortable working in a global company, delivering counsel and guidance to senior leadership in both Europe and within our HQ teams in the US. The successful candidate will have solid experience of creating internal advocacy among multiple senior audiences, as well as directing and inspiring a team of high performing communications professionals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Create, manage and drive the execution of the overarching communications strategy and plan, continuously aligning with the global and regional business and marketing strategies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Direct and oversee the development and execution of market plans supporting Corporate Communications, Policy Communications, and Consumer Communications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develop inspiring and compelling comms strategies to challenge the team and the business to achieve beyond our existing success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Provide strategic comms advice and counsel to our cross functional teams, collaborating with senior stakeholders from across the business (primarily Policy, Marketing, Business Operations) to work together to achieve goals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;12-15+ years of experience within high performing international organizations - either with agencies or in-house roles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A team leader with both a record of leading high performing comms teams, and experience of working with cross-functional teams to drive success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A proven history of encouraging and developing innovative industry-leading thinking and turning it into executable plans and campaigns&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Experience of operating in a high performing cross functional team, acting as counsel on all comms related matters and being proactive in elevating the work of comms across the region&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;A strong track record of developing inspiring goals that motivate team members to achieve personal and professional success&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Forward thinking, innovative and creative - proactively shares perspective at all levels of the organization&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Excellent problem solver with ability to anticipate future issues, unblock the most complex situations and facilitate drama-free environments where the team will thrive&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;German native speaker with fluent business English. Working knowledge of other languages within the region will be desirable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment To Inclusion &amp;amp; Belonging:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Airbnb is committed to working with the broadest talent pool possible. We believe diverse ideas foster innovation and engagement, and allow us to attract creatively-led people, and to develop the best products, services and solutions. All qualified individuals are encouraged to apply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;How We&#39;ll Take Care of You:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The actual base pay is dependent upon many factors, such as: training, transferable skills, work experience, business needs and market demands. The base pay range shown below is annualized, is subject to change and may be modified in the future. This role may also be eligible for bonus, benefits, and Employee Travel Credits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Germany Annual Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;€128.000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;€160.000 EUR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set up in 2017 in Gurgaon, Airbnb Capability Center was established to service the global Airbnb community. We are a fast-growing, up-and-coming office and home to the most hospitable people you will ever meet! Our small and extremely capable team of Gurgaon-based colleagues strive to make the impossible happen for our inbound and outbound travelers within this big and diverse market. ACC is providing varied services under Community Support thereby providing world-class customer experience to our customers. Besides this, ACC is also building deep capabilities for different verticals like GSS, Finance Technology Group, Finance Shared Services, Analytics etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Connectivity Integration Analyst, you will&amp;nbsp; work on API integrations and provide troubleshooting support, enhance operational efficiency by streamlining workflows, improving task prioritization, and fostering cross-functional collaboration. Through the creation of data-driven insights and innovative process automation, this position will drive informed decision-making and operational innovation. Additionally, by addressing tooling and process challenges with expert solutions and providing adaptable project support, the role will ensure operational excellence and contribute to the broader success of the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a key member of the operations team, you will leverage conceptual knowledge of principles, practices, and methodologies within an operational focus area, applying expertise across various workflows. Your role requires a combination of job-related training and extensive on-the-job experience to drive efficiency and effectiveness in daily operations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Subject Matter Expert:&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the primary technical liaison for hotels and partners integrating with Airbnb and HotelTonight via supported PMS, CMS, or Channel Managers, ensuring seamless onboarding, mapping, troubleshooting, and ongoing connectivity support—including test rollouts, issue resolution (such as XML data exchange and eligibility concerns), performance reporting, partner engagement, product bug escalation, internal training, and the creation of self-help resources to optimize partner experience and operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Working knowledge of technical tools:&lt;/strong&gt; Analyze &amp;amp; troubleshoot connectivity related issues including &lt;strong&gt;XML data&lt;/strong&gt; to ensure a seamless exchange of inventory &amp;amp; reservation data. Basic understanding and working knowledge of technical tools like Sumo Logic and Snowflake&amp;nbsp; would be an added advantage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leverage AI and Automation:&lt;/strong&gt; Champion the use of AI-driven tools and automation to optimize workflows, enhance data management, and streamline onboarding and daily operations. Identify opportunities where AI can improve efficiency, accuracy and the overall customer and partner experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Innovation and Problem Solving: &lt;/strong&gt;Drive innovation by proactively identifying complex business and technical challenges, designing creative solutions, and championing a culture of continuous improvement across teams. Leverage deep expertise to solve ambiguous problems, experiment with new approaches, and influence strategic decisions that elevate Airbnb’s products and services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Process Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead the identification, design and implementation of innovative process improvements for onboarding, data management, and cross-team collaboration. Utilize advanced analytics and automation, including AI-based solutions, to deliver scalable and sustainable outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Partner with Product, Engineering, Data Science and other stakeholder teams to resolve multi-faceted challenges, drive strategic initiatives, and continuously improve operational workflows across the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mentorship and Coaching:&lt;/strong&gt; Mentor and upskill team members by sharing subject matter expertise, supporting learning in content management, partner communications and AI-enabled operations; foster an inclusive and high-performing team culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Management :&lt;/strong&gt; Develop, manage, and present data-driven reports and dashboards, ensuring KPIs and operational objectives are consistently met or exceeded through evidence-based action planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Apply deep knowledge of how cross-functional teams&#39; efforts contribute to organizational objectives, proactively aligning team deliverables and priorities to maximize impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Change Agent:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead and support organizational transformation by advocating for and implementing new technologies, tools, and best practices, with a focus on continuous improvement and operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in a relevant field or equivalent practical experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expertise in leveraging AI, data analytics, and automation platforms (e.g., AI-powered workflow tools, SQL, Airtable, Google Suite, Python or similar) to transform business processes and solve complex challenges&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of progressive experience in Operations or related fields, with a proven track record of driving cross-functional initiatives and leading impactful projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideally, 2+ years background in working with Excel, XML and SQL. Great understanding of how APIs function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to communicate clearly and effectively with stakeholders on multiple levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have attention to detail and analytical skills to quickly detect and resolve problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a flexible mindset with the ability to handle constantly changing priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced knowledge of HotelTonight and/or hospitality industry processes, tools, and workflows, with demonstrated success in optimizing end-to-end operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional analytical, conceptual, and problem-solving abilities; able to synthesize information and anticipate future trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to work both independently and collaboratively, influencing and aligning multiple stakeholders to shared goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational, communication, and leadership skills, with the ability to convey complex information to diverse audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to continuous improvement, inclusive behaviors, and fostering a culture of innovation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agile, proactive, and resilient mindset; comfortable navigating and leading through ambiguity and change&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hybrid Work Requirements &amp;amp; Expectations: &lt;/strong&gt;To support productivity and maintain a professional hybrid work environment, employees are expected to adhere to the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Workspace&lt;/strong&gt;: A dedicated, quiet, and private workspace free from interruptions and external noise&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internet Connectivity&lt;/strong&gt;: During the working hours, maintain a minimum and consistent internet speed of 10 Mbps on your official devices to ensure reliability for work-related tasks, including calls and virtual meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Professionalism:&lt;/strong&gt; Employees must remain fully engaged, respectful, and maintain a professional presence during virtual meetings, with video participation required unless otherwise approved.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Confidentiality &amp;amp; Security:&lt;/strong&gt; Employees are responsible for protecting Airbnb’s Intellectual Property and Confidential Information. Work-related activities, including calls and meetings, must not be conducted in public places, while traveling, or in any setting that may compromise confidentiality or work quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment To Inclusion &amp;amp; Belonging&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Airbnb is committed to working with the broadest talent pool possible. We believe diverse ideas foster innovation and engagement, and allow us to attract creatively-led people, and to develop the best products, services and solutions. All qualified individuals are encouraged to apply.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;How We&#39;ll Take Care of You:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our job titles may span more than one career level. The actual base pay is dependent upon many factors, such as: training, transferable skills, work experience, business needs and market demands. The base pay range shown below is annualized, is inclusive of allowances and is subject to change and may be modified in the future. This role may also be eligible for bonus or incentives, one or more equity programs, benefits, and Employee Travel Credits.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;India Annual Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;₹1,050,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;₹1,500,000 INR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Highlights&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ability to speak English and Japanese is a required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No relocation and visa support&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Airbnb Hotels team is a fun, fast-growing group leading Airbnb’s expansion into the hotel sector. Operating with an entrepreneurial spirit, this team combines the simplicity, product excellence, and guest-centered ethos that define Airbnb. This team’s mission is to deliver the smoothest, most intuitive hotel booking experience for guests, while helping hotels easily drive incremental bookings so they can focus on delivering the best hospitality. The ultimate aim is to help more people discover high-quality hotels, creating value for guests and our hotel partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will build, manage, and grow strategic relationships with technical partners (like software providers or integrators) to drive mutual business growth, focusing on seamless API/system integrations, revenue generation, and aligning technical capabilities with supply strategy. This role requires strong relationship-building, technical acumen (especially for APIs/integrations), strategic thinking, and data analysis to identify opportunities, resolve complex issues, and ensure partners effectively leverage the company&#39;s platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive measurable business impact by managing stakeholders to achieve sales goals, including creating joint go-to-market (GTM) strategies, and expanding partner-driven revenue.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a subject matter expert for connectivity, providing technical support, troubleshooting API integrations, and ensuring technical alignment between partners and internal systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a deep understanding of technical integrations across Property Management Systems, Channel Managers, and Central Reservation Systems to provide targeted client support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use data to identify strategic opportunities and drive sales growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration: Work with Product, Engineering, Enterprise Accounts&amp;nbsp; and Field Operations teams to align partner initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate clients on product updates and share partner feedback with internal stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and oversee effective troubleshooting processes, escalating as needed&lt;br&gt;Identify patterns in data and feedback to improve services and products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support your team to define and execute the global connectivity roadmap and standards for the Hotels supply team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the development of technical communication materials such as policies, procedures, and presentations.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in a Connectivity or Technical Partner Manager role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years experience in a direct partner facing commercial account management role focused on strategic, complex, and high-value technical partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of hospitality/travel software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in SQL, Sumo Logic, and Excel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid technical troubleshooting skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and presentation abilities, with confidence in engaging stakeholders up to the C-level with prospective and existing partners across multiple channels including in person presentation skills.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective time management and ability to prioritize in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong quantitative skills with a proven ability to leverage data in decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adaptability to shifting priorities, projects, and deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for Airbnb, travel, and the sharing economy—being an Airbnb host is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ability to speak Japanese is a required&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

