&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The actual base pay is dependent upon many factors, such as: training, transferable skills, work experience, business needs and market demands. The base pay range shown below is annualized, is subject to change and may be modified in the future. This role may also be eligible for bonus, benefits, and Employee Travel Credits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;United Kingdom Annual Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;£70,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;£85,000 GBP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This opportunity is offered as a 12-month fixed term contract.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every day, Airbnb hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way. Since our founding, more than 5 million hosts have welcomed over 1.5 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Supply organization plays a pivotal role in driving the company’s growth and expansion efforts worldwide. This team recruits and develops Airbnb’s global supply of high-quality stays, Experiences, and Services. With this focus on quality supply and international expansion, the team is leading the way for Airbnb’s continued growth and facilitation of millions more host and guest connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Market Manager, you will be focused on bringing differentiated service products to life through acquiring untapped, unique supply in the services market to provide positive experiences for Guests and Hosts in your assigned territory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Focusing on these responsibilities, you will build Airbnb’s strong market presence in your assigned territory by collaborating with other teams as the local in-market expert. As someone who knows the Airbnb mission and values inside out, you will drive all phases of supply acquisition and market success, including acquisition strategy development, generating and converting supply leads, maintaining the experience quality, nurturing strategic relationships with hosts, as well as creating them from scratch. You will help develop and iterate scalable localized supply management strategies for both developed and highly competed market destinations and nascent and relatively untapped new markets ultimately ensuring our long-term market success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and manage partner relationships within assigned territory, with a strong emphasis on in-person relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to handle operational complexity and ability to maximize the impact of resources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Directly manage top-tier accounts to meet and exceed quarterly/annual sales goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze data and utilize data-driven recommendations to identify and action on strategic opportunities in your region to increase sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect and onboard new, high-quality supply in your assigned geography&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a baseline understanding of the technical integration of various software partners to provide the appropriate support to your clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop deep knowledge of Services partners and become the go-to source for all information relating to relevant market trends and market dynamics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work across Airbnb internal teams, including country managers, regional teams, and business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with strategic B2B partners to build long-term relationships&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate barriers, market shifts and trends, and lead proactive solution development; apply critical thinking to recommend standards and operating strategies that mitigate risk and propel growth given resource requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hold regular optimization calls and business reviews with your partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of relevant experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional ability to organize, lead and meticulously execute on large-scale projects with company-wide impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operates with a growth mindset and has a very strong bias for action&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interprets internal or external business issues and recommends best practices for the larger team and a strategic portfolio across distinct and varying market stages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to influence product, policy, and other cross functional stakeholders&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigates and overcomes organizational barriers by establishing trust, influencing decision-making, and bringing together diverse perspectives to drive alignment and progress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable and skilled at regularly interfacing with&amp;nbsp; senior management (Director, Regional Director)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilizes knowledge of key business drivers and the factors to drive results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Executes flawlessly and autonomously&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to handle operational complexity and ability to maximize the impact of resources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment To Inclusion &amp;amp; Belonging:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Airbnb is committed to working with the broadest talent pool possible. We believe diverse ideas foster innovation and engagement, and allow us to attract creatively-led people, and to develop the best products, services and solutions. All qualified individuals are encouraged to apply.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;How We&#39;ll Take Care of You:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Our job titles may span more than one career level. The actual base pay is dependent upon many factors, such as: training, transferable skills, work experience, business needs and market demands. The base pay range shown below is monthly, is subject to change and may be modified in the future. This role may also be eligible for bonus, benefits, and Employee Travel Credits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Mexico Monthly Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$100,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$125,000 MXN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission on Marketing Technology (MarTech) is to provide a state-of-the-art platform and measurement capabilities to enable marketing and product teams to engage with our customers effectively. Everyday millions of Airbnb customers are reached via our streamlined platform over comprehensive channels, such as Email, Push, SMS, and external Ads Platforms. We deliver substantial business impact by enabling numerous stakeholders across the company, including Marketing (Brand and Performance), Guest/Host, Policy, and more.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Marketing Technology Operations is part of a platform team responsible for building the signal infrastructure that powers advertising and measurement globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team deploys Airbnb’s unique first-party data to leading advertising platforms such as Meta, Google, and TikTok to power personalized, effective, and measurable marketing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are building systems that make marketing infrastructure increasingly autonomous — where tagging, validation, and signal delivery are highly automated and marketers can focus on strategy rather than operational execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Senior Marketing Technology Operations Manager with a strong foundation in marketing tracking who is excited about using AI and automation to build scalable marketing systems. This role will partner closely with engineering to design and build our next generation robust, and scalable tracking platform that minimizes manual intervention and maximizes signal quality and reliability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work at the intersection of marketing, data and engineering. Your work will ensure that our marketing teams can leverage rich first-party signals to drive efficient growth, improve measurement, and unlock new opportunities for experimentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are particularly excited about applying AI to marketing technology — from automating tag deployment and debugging to building systems that monitor signal health and detect issues automatically. This role is ideal for someone who is passionate about experimenting with AI tools, and improving complex marketing infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop solutions to upgrade our marketing tracking that minimize manual intervention while ensuring quality and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI tools to streamline and automate MarTech Ops responsibilities such as tag deployment, debugging, and monitoring signal health.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be hands on working in tag manager and our MMP to set up new ad vendors and QA marketing tracking.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with marketing and data science to deploy first party audiences for ad tracking and measurement.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up to date on global privacy frameworks and regulations (e.g., ATT, GDPR) to ensure all marketing tracking practices are compliant and uphold data integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of relevant work experience, ideally in a high-growth tech startup, performance-oriented marketing organization, or agency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with paid social and performance advertising platforms such as Meta and Google&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using AI tools to automate operational workflows&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with tag management systems such as Google Tag Manager, CAPI solutions and mobile measurement platforms such as Singular, AppsFlyer or Adjust&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical skills that can adapt to new tools and capabilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of how privacy frameworks and regulations (such as ATT and GDPR) impact marketing measurement and tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to lead, influence, and collaborate across organizational boundaries with a track record of building strong relationships with cross-functional partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for building systems that reduce manual work and allow teams to focus on higher-impact strategic initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience partnering closely with engineering teams to design scalable systems and automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness and ability to get into the technical weeds when troubleshooting complex issues across tracking systems, APIs, and data pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Current or previous experience being an Airbnb host is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;This position is US - Remote Eligible. The role may include occasional work at an Airbnb office or attendance at offsites, as agreed to with your manager. While the position is Remote Eligible, you must live in a state where Airbnb, Inc. has a registered entity. &lt;a style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot; href=&quot;https://careers.airbnb.com/&quot;&gt;Click here for the up-to-date list of excluded states. This list is continuously evolving, so please check back with us if the state you live in is on the exclusion list&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;If your position is employed by another Airbnb entity, your recruiter will inform you what states you are eligible to work from.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
