&lt;li&gt;KubeCon+CloudNativeCon 2024, Link:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lAUmdIGP_fE&quot;&gt;DNS deep dive in k8s with CoreDNS&lt;/a&gt;, Jingming Guo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Airbnb Tech Blog 2023, Link: &lt;a href=&quot;https://medium.com/airbnb-engineering/improving-istio-propagation-delay-d4da9b5b9f90&quot;&gt;Improving Istio Propagation Delay&lt;/a&gt;, Ying Zhu&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
